snippet.title: SpongeBob's Truth or Square (Game Trailer; 2009)
snippet.description: With the help of his friends, SpongeBob must use Plankton's memory machine to retrace the happiest moments of his life to find the Krabby Patty formula in time for the Krusty Krab's Eleventy Seventh anniversary.
